metadata.name: The March
metadata.description:
“The armies of the past, the armies of the present! 
The vows taken, the promises broken! 
God is with us in our endeavors, God is with us in our endeavors!” they chanted. 

Pink Skies is an attempt at discovering the dream-state in the ordinary. It’s a platonic exploration of the familiar/distant in the so-very-close. Each photograph was taken at a different time and place, but all share the same sensibility. The slippery state of the columns of reality. 

#1

St. Petersburg
2019
Edition 1/1
3456 x 3456
